WEBVTT

00:00:00.140 --> 00:00:03.060
=The Crow Princess of Fortune=

00:00:03.060 --> 00:00:04.980
=Episode 9=

00:00:08.540 --> 00:00:10.019
Spare me!

00:00:10.020 --> 00:00:10.979
I don't want to die!

00:00:10.980 --> 00:00:12.779
They're going to grind me into powder

00:00:12.780 --> 00:00:14.219
and mix me into Prince Jing's food.

00:00:14.220 --> 00:00:16.120
They said once he eats it,
his limbs will go weak,

00:00:16.120 --> 00:00:17.019
he'll lose all feeling,

00:00:17.020 --> 00:00:18.299
and become a cripple forever.

00:00:18.300 --> 00:00:19.659
I was forced into this too!

00:00:19.660 --> 00:00:20.619
Oh?

00:00:20.620 --> 00:00:22.419
Is that true?

00:00:22.420 --> 00:00:24.139
Every word is true.

00:00:24.140 --> 00:00:25.819
Please save me, Young Mistress.

00:00:25.820 --> 00:00:27.699
I don't want to be ground into powder!

00:00:27.700 --> 00:00:30.340
So they're planning to use poison
to harm your father.

00:00:32.020 --> 00:00:33.300
Don't worry.

00:00:33.340 --> 00:00:35.860
I'm a compassionate person.

00:00:36.100 --> 00:00:37.940
But...

00:00:39.420 --> 00:00:40.219
Uh...

00:00:40.220 --> 00:00:41.939
Will this really work?

00:00:41.940 --> 00:00:43.379
Just do as you're told.

00:00:43.380 --> 00:00:44.619
Once it's done,

00:00:44.620 --> 00:00:47.580
I'll reward you
with a basket of fresh leaves.

00:00:47.620 --> 00:00:48.860
Deal.

00:01:08.420 --> 00:01:09.540
Prince Jing,

00:01:10.140 --> 00:01:13.620
this soup was specially prepared
by the imperial kitchen for you.

00:01:13.820 --> 00:01:16.860
It was simmered for three days and nights
with twenty four rare delicacies.

00:01:16.980 --> 00:01:18.020
Try it.

00:01:35.180 --> 00:01:37.780
Xiao Heng, what do you mean by this?

00:01:38.220 --> 00:01:39.820
Do you think Mother would poison you?

00:01:40.180 --> 00:01:41.780
How ungrateful.

00:01:48.100 --> 00:01:49.940
Your Highness is right.

00:01:50.340 --> 00:01:52.740
Mother would never poison me.

00:01:53.700 --> 00:01:56.420
But Mother always taught me

00:01:56.740 --> 00:01:58.940
to save the best things
for my younger brother.

00:01:59.500 --> 00:02:01.700
I've always remembered that.

00:02:02.140 --> 00:02:05.340
Since the Crown Prince
values Mother's kindness so much,

00:02:06.620 --> 00:02:07.500
please.

00:02:09.700 --> 00:02:10.339
You...

00:02:10.340 --> 00:02:11.540
Enough.

00:02:11.860 --> 00:02:13.620
There's soup for everyone.

00:02:13.700 --> 00:02:14.620
Serve it.

00:02:31.180 --> 00:02:33.579
(I knew Xiao Heng
wouldn't let his guard down.)

00:02:33.580 --> 00:02:35.619
(Good thing I came prepared.)

00:02:35.620 --> 00:02:37.780
(Let's see how he refuses this time.)

00:02:38.660 --> 00:02:40.780
You're so filial, Uncle.

00:02:41.060 --> 00:02:42.869
No matter what Grandma gives you,

00:02:42.870 --> 00:02:44.900
you'll definitely finish it all, right?

00:02:45.100 --> 00:02:47.460
Hmph. Of course.

00:02:47.980 --> 00:02:49.779
I never refuse anything

00:02:49.780 --> 00:02:51.460
Mother gives me.

00:02:52.540 --> 00:02:54.339
(There's no poison in my bowl anyway.)

00:02:54.340 --> 00:02:55.339
(What am I afraid of?)

00:02:55.340 --> 00:02:56.539
Are you sure?

00:02:56.540 --> 00:02:58.460
You said it yourself.

00:02:58.620 --> 00:02:59.460
Hmph.

00:03:06.100 --> 00:03:07.419
Help!

00:03:07.420 --> 00:03:08.659
Help!

00:03:08.660 --> 00:03:09.979
Get it away from me!

00:03:09.980 --> 00:03:11.420
Take it away!

00:03:17.020 --> 00:03:17.820
You!

00:03:18.060 --> 00:03:19.580
You harmed my son!

00:03:19.740 --> 00:03:21.459
Did I do something wrong?

00:03:21.460 --> 00:03:22.359
I only

00:03:22.360 --> 00:03:25.019
let Uncle try

00:03:25.020 --> 00:03:27.220
the good things you prepared for Father.

00:03:27.620 --> 00:03:29.380
Was I wrong?

00:03:30.060 --> 00:03:31.780
You did well.

00:03:31.940 --> 00:03:33.660
But let me tell you,

00:03:33.980 --> 00:03:35.899
next time there's something this good,

00:03:35.900 --> 00:03:38.220
don't forget to give
your grandma a share too.

00:03:39.460 --> 00:03:40.900
You...

00:03:41.340 --> 00:03:44.340
Men! Seize this demon girl!

00:03:46.100 --> 00:03:47.780
I'd like to see who dares!

00:03:49.940 --> 00:03:51.820
You...

00:03:53.460 --> 00:03:55.780
You actually brought
a weapon into the palace!

00:03:55.820 --> 00:03:57.460
As a military commander,

00:03:57.500 --> 00:03:58.459
I carry my sword in court

00:03:58.460 --> 00:03:59.820
with Father's permission.

00:03:59.900 --> 00:04:01.860
If you don't believe me,

00:04:01.900 --> 00:04:03.660
feel free to ask Father yourself.

00:04:04.140 --> 00:04:05.260
You...

00:04:05.660 --> 00:04:07.100
Fine.

00:04:07.740 --> 00:04:09.700
Fine, very fine!

00:04:10.380 --> 00:04:12.060
Then I'll arrest both of you.

00:04:12.700 --> 00:04:14.180
Let's see

00:04:14.980 --> 00:04:18.020
how tough you two really are.

00:04:18.660 --> 00:04:19.940
Men!

00:04:20.340 --> 00:04:21.980
Seize them both!

00:04:25.820 --> 00:04:27.220
Father, be careful!

00:04:54.560 --> 00:04:57.879
♪Little lucky star,
twinkling with a wink at me♪

00:04:57.880 --> 00:05:01.719
♪Every Chinese New Year day brings
the luckiest fortune slip♪

00:05:01.720 --> 00:05:05.239
♪The God of Wealth favors me,
the Matchmaker ties red strings for me♪

00:05:05.240 --> 00:05:08.200
♪With firecrackers going off,
good things keep coming one after another♪

00:05:09.080 --> 00:05:12.719
♪Make a wish on the very first day
of the Chinese New Year♪

00:05:12.720 --> 00:05:16.480
♪By the second day,
my belly's already round♪

00:05:16.560 --> 00:05:19.879
♪Always talking about dieting,
but the chub never disappears♪

00:05:19.880 --> 00:05:23.920
♪Good food brings joy
and happiness every single day♪

00:05:29.520 --> 00:05:33.199
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
every year is filled with joy♪

00:05:33.200 --> 00:05:36.839
♪I'm bringing blessings to everyone♪

00:05:36.840 --> 00:05:40.559
♪Hands clasped together in greeting♪

00:05:40.560 --> 00:05:44.199
♪May every family be sweet and happy♪

00:05:44.200 --> 00:05:47.879
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
may everything go your way♪

00:05:47.880 --> 00:05:49.799
♪Endlessly flowing♪

00:05:49.800 --> 00:05:56.000
♪Good fortune♪